NOVEMBER 2008: Began development on application framework, trading API's and IDE's for options traders (and stock, future, fx, spot)... including arbitrage/physical/contract/technical/swing, and other strategy-based traders.....
I started Development on what is now called MARKETAPI in 2008 after leaving RootZOO.com [very popular sports social network] where I was CTO and 1 of the 3 original co-founders) the 3rd original co-founder CTO since late 2006, and w departing from CTO co-founding position I held since late 2006 (to March 2008) at RootZOO.com, a sports social network and point-incentivized website and community discussion forum, and way more for sports fans.
ally was called StockAPI.com, but events and courses changed (and interests) towards *all* market aspects and data sources, (and trading) -- especially options and futures and options on futures. Hence the change to MARKETAPI, as it is barely just limited to stocks anymore.
